	"Action": "EditData",
	"Target": "Data/Events/Saloon",
	"Entries": {
		"{{ModID}}_PM7H/Friendship {{PeiMing}} 1750/HostOrLocalMail {{ModID}}_PM7HSaloonLetter/SawEvent {{ModID}}_PM6H/Weather rainy/DayOfWeek Sat Sun/Time 1800 2400": "continue/-1000 -1000/farmer 14 24 0 {{PeiMing}} 14 21 2/setSkipActions MarkEventSeen current {{ModID}}_PM7H/addConversationTopic {{ModID}}_PM7HCT/skippable/addTemporaryActor Gus 16 32 12 18 2 true Character/addTemporaryActor Emily 16 32 10 18 2 true Character/addTemporaryActor Elliott 16 32 16 23 1 true Character/viewport 14 24 clamp false unfreeze/pause 200/
		speed farmer 4/speed {{PeiMing}} 3/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"@! I am happy you made it here.\"/pause 300/emote farmer 32/pause 500/speak {{PeiMing}} \"We have a table. Let's go get a seat.\"/pause 200/advancedMove {{PeiMing}} false -2 0 4 10  0 -1 3 10 -7 0 2 10 0 2 3 10 -2 0 4 10 0 -1 3 10 -2 0 2 10 0 1 2 100/advancedMove farmer false 0 -1 4 10 -11 0 3 1000/waitForAllStationary/
		proceedPosition {{PeiMing}}/speed Emily 4/
		advancedMove Emily false 0 -1 -4 0 0 5 -3 0 3 200/
		textAboveHead {{PeiMing}} \"Enjoyable atmosphere...\"/pause 300/emote farmer 56/pause 500/waitForAllStationary/
		speak Emily \"Hi! What can I get you two?\"/pause 200/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"One of your beers for me, please.\"/pause 200/
		quickQuestion \"What would you like, friend? It's on me.\"#\"Some beer, please!\"#\"I'd like some juice.\"(break)pause 100\\speak Emily \"Beer? Coming right up!\"\\switchEvent {{ModID}}_PM7HPickedBeer(break)pause 100\\speak Emily \"Some juice? I'll be back with your orders in a moment!\"\\switchEvent {{ModID}}_PM7HPickedJuice",

		"{{ModID}}_PM7HPickedBeer": "pause 200/advancedMove Emily false 3 0 4 10 0 -5 1 10 4 0 2 10 0 1 2 100/waitForAllStationary/playSound glug/textAboveHead {{PeiMing}} \"I really like the beer here.\"/pause 1000/advancedMove Emily false 0 -1 -4 0 0 5 -3 0 3 200/waitForAllStationary/pause 400/speak Emily \"There you go! Two beers!\"/pause 200/addObject 1 22 (O)346 1/addObject 2 22 (O)346 1/addItem (O)346/pause 200/switchEvent {{ModID}}_PM7HContinue",

		"{{ModID}}_PM7HPickedJuice": "pause 200/advancedMove Emily false 3 0 4 10 0 -5 1 10 4 0 2 10 0 1 2 100/waitForAllStationary/playSound glug/textAboveHead {{PeiMing}} \"I really like the beer here.\"/pause 1000/advancedMove Emily false 0 -1 -4 0 0 5 -3 0 3 200/waitForAllStationary/pause 400/speak Emily \"There you go! One beer and one juice!\"/pause 200/addObject 1 22 (O)346 1/addObject 2 22 (O)350 1/addItem (O)350/pause 200/switchEvent {{ModID}}_PM7HContinue",	
		
		"{{ModID}}_PM7HContinue": "pause 200/emote farmer 32/pause 200/pause 500/emote Emily 56/pause 500/textAboveHead {{PeiMing}} \"You have my gratitude.\"/textAboveHead Emily \"Let me know if you need anything else.\"/advancedMove Emily false 3 0 4 10 0 -5 1 10 4 0 2 10 0 1 2 100/pause 300/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"Do enjoy your drink then.\"/pause 300/
		emote {{PeiMing}} 40/pause 500/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"I assume you followed my invitation because you wished to hear the rest of the story I began telling you the other day, huh?\"/pause 300/stopMusic/
		emote farmer 32/pause 500/textAboveHead {{PeiMing}} \"Alright... where did I stop...\"/pause 1000/playMusic {{ModID}}_ArukasBloom/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"I remember now. #$b# Last thing I told you was that I was on a mission and encountered a strange rift.\"/pause 500/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"While I was speaking to my friend to get information on this rift, something leaped out of one of these ripples and attacked me!$8#$b# I have no idea what this thing was but let me tell you, @, #$b# you can't just attack the General Ming Guang and think you will get out unscathed! $5\"/pause 500/removeObject 1 22/pause 300/{{BeerAnimation}}/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"I battled this creature without breaking a sweat, but... #$b# this thing was just so infuriating to deal with and hard to get rid of.#$b# Worse than these two kids here sometimes, I swear!$8\"/pause 300/emote farmer 28/pause 500/
		faceDirection Emily 1/pause 100/faceDirection Gus 3/
		emote Emily 8/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"Regardless, I stabbed it straight through its chest, cut off its head and got it off of me. #$b# A quick job, I told myself. #$b# But nooo, of course it wasn't, otherwise I wouldn't have ended up here, now, would I?\"/pause 100/
		textAboveHead Gus \"Quite the long tale.\"/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"Once again I tried to connect to my friend to give her a report, hoping she'd know more.\"/pause 500/
		textAboveHead Emily \"Scary, exciting and long.\"/pause 300/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"But then, I felt a sharp pain in my side. Like a needle drilling into your skin, but worse.$7\"/pause 300/
		jump farmer 5/emote farmer 16/pause 500/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"The thing was still alive. #$b# While I was busy trying to push it on the ground and squash it, it materialized one of these ripples right behind me.\"/pause 200/
		quickQuestion \"I didn't notice it on time and...\"#\"So you fell into it just like that?\"#\"And this is how you landed here?\"(break)pause 50\\emote {{PeiMing}} 28\\speak {{PeiMing}} \"H-hey now. I'll let you know that my fighting prowess is top notch most of the time. #$b# I got distracted for one second, and that was enough—#$b# come on, everyone makes mistakes sometimes!$8\"\\pause 300\\emote farmer 28(break)speak {{PeiMing}} \"Precisely. I like how you're fast to catch on, @ I appreciate that in you.$6\"\\emote farmer 32/pause 500/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"I must say, even as someone who lived as long as I have, I have never faced something like that. #$b# A rift in space and time...#$b# I would find it interesting if it wasn't me to suffer the consequences of that!\"/pause 300/stopAnimation {{PeiMing}}/
		textAboveHead Emily \"I feel sorry for him...\"/pause 300/
		emote {{PeiMing}} 12/pause 200/emote farmer 8/pause 500/
		jump {{PeiMing}} 3/textAboveHead {{PeiMing}} \"So many questions and no answers at all...\"/pause 1200/
		jump {{PeiMing}} 5/textAboveHead {{PeiMing}} \"and they just keep pilling up!\"/pause 1000/
		emote farmer 28/pause 500/
		quickQuestion \"...Mh. I apologize for losing my temper. All of this is very frustrating to me.\"#\"I get it. But you're not alone in this - I can help! We could ask the Wizard!\"#\"Maybe punching a tree would help?\"(break)pause 50\\speak {{PeiMing}} \"Help? Isn't that a daring thing to say?#$b# But I must admit, I am quite…  intrigued by your boldness, @.$3\"(break)pause 50\\emote {{PeiMing}} 32\\pause 300\\speak {{PeiMing}} \"HAH! $9 #$b# If I were to punch a tree, I think the Wizard would curse me, and trust me, @...#$b# At this point, I have enough curses for at least a century.\"/stopMusic/
		pause 500/textAboveHead {{PeiMing}} \"........................\"/{{BeerAnimation}}/pause 1000/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"Hmm... Perhaps we can actually ask the Wizard, yes. #$b# ...Thank you, @. Talking about it to you... #$b# Helped me get it out off my chest. I appreciate it.\"/pause 300/
		emote farmer 56/pause 500/
		speak {{PeiMing}} \"I will stay here for a bit longer. Gather my thoughts. The tab is on me, of course. #$b# See you around the town, eh? $3\"/pause 300/
		emote farmer 32/pause 500/viewport 3 23 clamp false/
		advancedMove farmer false 11 0 2 10 0 1 2 10/playSound thudStep/waitForAllStationary/warp farmer 999 999/pause 200/playSound thudStep/speed Elliott 4/
		advancedMove Elliott false -13 0 3 200/waitForAllStationary/pause 200/
		textAboveHead Elliott \"Hey there.\"/pause 1200/textAboveHead Elliott \"Let's have a drink or two.\"/pause 1000/
		textAboveHead {{PeiMing}} \"Ha!\"/pause 1200/textAboveHead {{PeiMing}} \"Sure, why not.\"/pause 1000/
		globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end"
		
	}
